OL,5, A man who was abused by monks at a     
OL,6, school in Fife run by Christian        
OL,7, Brothers has secured #1.4m in damages. 
OL,9,FIt is believed to be the highest sum   
OL,10,Fever to be awarded to a survivor.      
OL,12,FThe victim was sexually assaulted and  
OL,13,Fbeaten by three Christian Brothers     
OL,14,Fwhile staying at St Ninian's School in 
OL,15,FFalkland in 1980 and 81.               
OL,17,FThe man, who was named in courts as AB 
OL,18,Fto protect his identity, said he hoped 
OL,19,Fhis award would inspire others in their
OL,20,Fquest for justice.                     
